title: Myslym Alla
text: Myslym 'Lym' Alla (15 April 1919 – 1 January 1999) was an Albanian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player and manager who played for <a href="SK%20Tirana">SK Tirana</a> and went on to manage <a href="SK%20Tirana">17 Nëntori</a> and <a href="Partizani%20Tirana">Partizani Tirana</a>.
